Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:04.33,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\q1}\n\n\n\n\n三月9日 Diamandra監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙手抱頭！ 退後！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是403號吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賭一把嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭她能夠逃多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只能順著管道跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是逃不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 會走的更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那個傢伙的話 絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SB們！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢追老娘的屁股！ 做好覺悟了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價可不便宜哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,403號 Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無意投降 就將你當場擊斃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:47.86,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(950,395)\fs45}再見了！無情的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.48,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}      三月10日 橘子鎮(Laranja)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月10日 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晨6時起床 我最早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}越獄事件發生已經過了一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}從重兵把守、被譽為不可能逃脫的 Diamandra重刑犯特別監獄逃脫的是囚犯michiko malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}乘著昨夜的狂風天氣 隱藏行蹤 至今仍未被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有我是外人的家 這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包飯 低鹽量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋殼掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro神父和他的妻子Johanna
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹頭徹尾的虛假父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 這個孩子在欺瞞我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 不要成為隱藏失敗的不成器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣冠冕堂皇地讓我重做蛋包飯 這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maria姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maria 這個名字有點問題(一點不像聖母)...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.01,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gabriel:大天使之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gabriel弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Belenbauza Yamada家的諸位成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、Hana的一天就這樣開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要為妻子和孩子們的健康向主表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大體上(早餐)就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(200,200)}土豆鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.89,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}鼻屎＝鼻（はな/Hana）くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 鼻屎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這往下是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就在海裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撿！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水裏面是走不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水裏能呼吸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些黑斑到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桶的水被我弄翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道值多少錢嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己是小孩子就會被原諒 在我這裏是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾是用來擦身體的 不是用來穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抓了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情天天發生 看不到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 利索點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則打你個腦門開花、血漿四濺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:39.00,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Banco Do Brasil:巴西銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月15日 今天政府的人會來察看我的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只是來看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下錢就走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.51,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}圣佩德羅教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 我將這些贈與你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.48,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ciencia:科學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 還記得今天早晨的新聞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏 像你這樣的孩子不出賣身體或內臟就無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你從水深火熱之中拯救出來的是誰？ 你明白吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是... 主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是... 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:26.57,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}語出新約馬太福音5:43 原文"Ye have heard that it hath been said,Thou shalt love thy neighbour,and hate thine enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要有怨恨 "愛你的鄰居"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人剛剛收買了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Maria的舊書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.91,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在巴拉伊鎮發生銀行搶劫的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:49.12,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯人是日前從Diamandra重刑犯特別監獄逃跑的 Michiko Malandro可能性非常高...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去很舒服啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是信徒的佈施 談不上什麼價格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像過得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸甚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道"Debody of the year"嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是什麼 debo... dy？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅頒發給作出傑出貢獻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公被選中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫Gonzalez的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常棘手的壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我老公一番佈道就把他馴服了 現在他可是優秀的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.07,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a7}五個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gonzalez是因為腦子裏還殘留著子彈才會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gonzalez 主說已經原諒了你的所有作為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野貓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 是Maria撿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它真的是很疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco在大便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧Blanco的事情能不能換人 早晨開始我就頭暈的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是誰值日？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有增加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道養一個孩子要花多少錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個給我扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.71,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}  三月16日 Belenbauza家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 說起來早上沒有看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨晚起就沒有看見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看見你把它帶出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco的速度更快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco二世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不覺得髒嗎？ 這只Blanco
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了Gabriel 我有好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco是白色的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須弄乾淨些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 馴馬 馴馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 給我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒做！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我作對是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們家也不需要像你這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被耍來耍去 知道我在想什麼嗎！ 知道我在看什麼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老娘記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:17:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕一個人回去 本想帶Blanco一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從道路的遠處有人會來迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Belen什麼的Yamada的家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是的... 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫Hana的小鬼在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早我去接她 給我準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 您是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 好像是Hana的母親會來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親不是死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妒忌我的地位的傢伙的伎倆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.68,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Certificado de adocao de menor:未成年人收養證書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消減養育費讓我為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把獵槍拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向這些傢伙反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.33,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a5}   三月17日 Belenbauza家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方把Hana藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你 四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎？ Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 一直盯著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半張著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.77,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}L.B.D.D.:葡萄牙語“自由”的縮寫(liberdade)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 別給我裝啞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰會來迎接我 我一直期祈求著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月17日的早晨 那個人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個人 到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}待續
